page.title: 12BROWNIES
page.content: BROWNIES IS HELD ON THURSDAY NIGHT AT 5:30 P.M.7.OO P.M. AT THE LAST BROWNIE MEETING WE MADE A BALLOON PENCIL HOLDERS. YOU DO THINGS FOR BADGES AT BROWNIES.I LIKE GOING TO BROWNIES. ON COLLET DAY WE HAD A STALL. AT SOME MEETINGS MY SIX ARE NAUGHTY AT BROWNIES. ONE WEEK WE WENT TO THE PARK. AT BROWNIES SOME TIMES WE MAKE THINGS AND SOME TIMES WE GO OUT FOR WALKS OR TO PLAY GAMES.ON OUR WALKS WE HAVE TO FIND THINGS E.G FIR-CONES FIOWERS,AND LEAVES. OUTSIDE WE SOMETIMES HAVE RACES. WHEN WE STAY INSIDE WE PLAY GAMES E.G. BAKED BEAHS.SOMETIMES WE MAKE THINGS.
